						               													<description>Description from the designer:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Organizing an appealing carnival parade is not an easy task. To play a beautiful role on the parade, the job in the shed of samba schools must be arduous and only the most competent players will succeed!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game Ziriguidum brings the challenge behind the scenes of organizing a samba school parade, in a very thematic, fun and strategic way. Players need to make the right decisions about design and execution of the sections of their school, about the amount of tests, solving unexpected events, always seeking to please the judges in order to get the best ratings at the end of the parade.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ziriguidum is a eurogame of medium complexity, which entertains both casual and experienced players. Its main mechanicss are card drafting and hand management. The game supports 2 to 6 players, and lasts about 60 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Prepare your costumes and tambourines to make a unique and impressive spetacle!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
